# Changelog

## [0.4.1] - 2021-07-30

(only updated requirements and minimal cleanup)


## [0.4.0] - 2020-12-06

### Changed
- reworked all callbacks to make code cleaner and easier to handle

### Fixed
- added missing validation, which broke some session-creations


### Changed
- reworked all callbacks

## [0.3.0] - 2020-12-01

### Added
- support for unix-domain-sockets
- source-code comments

### Changed
- creating a server is now optional
- updated callbacks for new session and stream-messages
- input-values now have to be set as string instead of data-map for easier message-forwaring


## [0.2.1] - 2020-10-18

### Added
- event-queue for incoming trigger-messages to avoid timeouts in the session-layer and to avoid race-conditions while processing multiple messages at once


## [0.2.0] - 2020-10-11

### Changed
- update to handle the results coming from the new libKitsunemimiSakuraLang v0.7.0 and send these results over the network.


## [0.1.0] - 2020-10-08

### Added
- first basic version to trigger sakura-tree over network

